bnagladic (s [[tutlayt tabngalt]]: বাংলাদেশ) s ism unṣib tagduda n bangladic taɣrfant (Gônoprojatontri Bangladesh)  tzga dg unẓul ugmuḍ n  umnẓaw n [[asya]]. g iwtta nns tlla [[lhind]]  d  [[myanmar]] d uftas n [[bngal]].  ism n bngal yddad sg tutlayt tabngalit anamk nns "tamurt n bangal".

tga  bangladic tamurt tiss sat dg umaḍal g uṭṭun n  imzdaɣn 
tuɣal bngladic dffir azarug nns tamurt tabrlamanit tamgdut d iga  mujib ɛbd raḥman aslway n inɣlafn g usggas 1973 , . dffir istayn ylla laẓ g marra timnaḍin n tmurt g  usggas 1973 d 1974 dg tzwara n usggas 1975 yssnti mujib ɛbd raḥman usnulfu n ukabar amaynu nn yskr ism nns  Baksal nna igan asdukkl  jar  tirni n awamilik d ukabar n kricak sramik nna ittalɣn  [[mujib ɛbd raḥman]]  g bngladic.

g smmus d mraw g wayyur n ɣuct g usggas 1975، ittwanɣa mujib  d ayt twacult nns ɣaf ufus n trbiɛt n iḍubbaṭn  isrdasn.
==akcam n lislam==
ykcm [[lislam]] ɣr lbangal g tasut tiss snat d mraw   xf ubrid n imzznzitn  imuslmn    yttuga unurẓm  n lislam  g ufsar nns g maṛṛa timnaḍin g tmurt. amɣar  aturki [[baktir xiliji]]   ysluzza blakcman sin , nna igan yiwn sg twacult n ihindusn  (Senaa) .
g  tasut tis sḍist d mraw، tnbaḍ [[tambṛaṭurt tamagulit]] tamnaḍt n bngal tuɣal daka yiwn sg  wammasn ixatarn n tmhla   tamagulit.








